\subsection{Base field of a Belyi map}
\begin{definition}\label{belyi.base_field}
\uses{belyi.galmap}
The **base field** of a {{KNOWL('belyi.galmap', 'Belyi map')}} $\phi:X\to\mathbb{P}^1$ is the field $X$ and $\phi$ are defined over.  
(In the database, we take this base field to be the field of moduli whenever possible.)
\end{definition}


